{
  "texts": [
    "The responses were anonymized and formatted uniformly in plain text to prevent raters from identifying the chatbot source.",
    "These responses were then randomized and presented to pediatricians for evaluation.",
    "The evaluation process was structured in three stages, conducted on separate dates with a 48-hour gap between each to minimize any potential carryover effects.",
    "Accuracy evaluationIn our research, the role of the evaluator was lled by Ying Li, a pediatrician with over two decades of clinical experience.",
    "To ensure impartiality, the identity of each LLM-Chatbot was kept hidden from the evaluator."
  ]
}